title: Trial begins for veterans of 2012 Ron Paul campaign
text: DES MOINES — Three figures in the "liberty movement" built by former representative Ron Paul of Texas will finally go on trial today, nearly four years after an alleged scheme to bribe an Iowa state senator into switching his presidential campaign endorsement. According to the federal indictment, which a grand jury handed down shortly before the first 2016 Republican […] ...
